p: We also found upregulated genes that integrate extracellular matrix organization, interferon signaling, interleukin signaling, and integrin cell surface interaction, including ITGAM, VCAM1, ICAM1 in Reactome enrichment (Fig. 3). The transcriptome results were coherent with the cell growth assay that results in progressive reduction in the numbers of growing TEC, reduced cell proliferation and cell division, with a slight increase of apoptosis after ZIKV infection (Supplemental Table 2 and Fig. 2).
